items.headline: Maple Leafs at Rangers
items.seoTitle: Toronto Maple Leafs New York Rangers game preview
items.seoDescription: MAPLE LEAFS (24-9-3) at RANGERS (25-10-4)7:30 p.m. ET; TNT, SN, TVAS, NHL LIVE
items.seoKeywords: news, nhl, hockey, projected lineups, starting goalies, Toronto Maple Leafs, New York Rangers, game preview
items.preview:
MAPLE LEAFS (24-9-3) at RANGERS (25-10-4)

7:30 p.m. ET; TNT, SN, TVAS, NHL LIVE

items.title: Broadcast Start
items.description: Broadcast Start

items.title: Period Start
items.description: Period Start

items.title: Goal
items.description: Ilya Mikheyev (6) Wrist Shot, assists: Pierre Engvall (9)

highlight.title: Mikheyev continues hot streak
highlight.blurb: TOR@NYR: Mikheyev scores 6th goal in last 8 games
highlight.description: Ilya Mikheyev capitalizes from the front door off Kyle Clifford's rebound with a wrist shot to give Toronto their first goal of the night

items.title: Goal
items.description: Mitchell Marner (8) Snap Shot, assists: William Nylander (21), John Tavares (21)

highlight.title: Marner sneaks in PPG in the 1st
highlight.blurb: TOR@NYR: Marner breaks his PPG drought
highlight.description: Just 46 seconds after Ilya Mikheyev's goal, William Nylander finds Mitch Marner across the ice for a slick pass to give Marner a PPG

items.title: Goal
items.description: Ryan Reaves (1) Wrist Shot, assists: Greg McKegg (3), Adam Fox (35)

highlight.title: Reaves nets 1st goal with Rangers
highlight.blurb: TOR@NYR: Reaves cuts the Leafs' lead in half
highlight.description: Greg McKegg sets up Ryan Reaves in front of the net as he settles in to rip his 50th career goal and first as a Ranger

items.title: Goal
items.description: Michael Bunting (9) Wrist Shot, assists: Auston Matthews (16), Mitchell Marner (17)

highlight.title: Bunting scores off odd-man rush
highlight.blurb: TOR@NYR: Bunting knocks one in off a rebound
highlight.description: Toronto's top line cashes in on an odd-man rush as Michael Bunting knocks in the Leafs' third goal of the period off a rebound

highlight.title: Reaves puts home his 2nd goal
highlight.blurb: TOR@NYR: Reaves put Rangers within 1 in the 2nd
highlight.description: Ryan Reaves nets his second goal of the game off the missed wide shot by K'Andre Miller, putting the Rangers within one of the Leafs

items.title: Shot
items.description: Mitchell Marner Tip-In saved by Igor Shesterkin

items.description: Adam Fox (6) Wrist Shot, assists: Ryan Strome (21), Artemi Panarin (29)

highlight.title: Fox's wrister ties it
highlight.blurb: TOR@NYR: Strome to Fox equalizes in the 2nd
highlight.description: Artemi Panarin finds Ryan Strome down low as he sets Adam Fox up for a slick wrist shot to tie the game in the late 2nd period
